        <item>
            <title>Neuralink 首宗人類大腦植入晶片手術   Elon Musk：患者狀況良好 + 技術有前景</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/30/neuralink-first-implant-of-chips-in-human-brain/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=neuralink-first-implant-of-chips-in-human-brain</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/30/neuralink-first-implant-of-chips-in-human-brain/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 05:27:15 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Elon Musk]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Neuralink]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[晶片]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1217716</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Elon Musk 稍早前在 X （前稱 Twitter）發文，表示旗下大腦晶片公司 Neuralink 已完成首例人類腦部植入晶片手術，Elon Musk 指患者目前狀況良好，又表示：「初步結果顯示，脈衝神經元檢測很有前景。」</p><p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">The first human received an implant from <a href="https://twitter.com/neuralink?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Neuralink</a> yesterday and is recovering well.<br><br>Initial results show promising neuron spike detection.</p>&mdash; Elon Musk (@elonmusk) <a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1752098683024220632?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 29, 2024</a></blockquote><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></p><p>Neurlink 上年 5 月經已獲美國食品及藥物管理局（ Food and Drug Administration，FDA）批准進行人體大腦植入晶片實驗。其後 Neuralink 於同年 9 月宣佈開始招募 22 歲以上，患有四肢癱瘓和肌萎縮側索硬化症 (ALS) 的志願者，進行「大腦晶片植入」臨牀實驗。</p><p>Elon Musk 曾經形容 Neuralink 晶片為「頭骨內的 Fitbit」。Elon Musk 另外又指 Neualink 正開發視覺晶片，將會在數年內面世，以幫助失明人士重見光明。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://neurosciencenews.com/neuralink-human-implant-22542/">Neuro Science News</a>、<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/elon-musk-says-first-human-patient-has-received-brain-implant">Bloomberg</a>、<a href="https://www.reuters.com/technology/neuralink-implants-brain-chip-first-human-musk-says-2024-01-29/">Reuters</a>、<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2024/jan/29/elon-musk-neuralink-first-human-brain-chip-implant">The Guardian</a>、<a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2024/01/29/elon-musks-neuralink-implants-brain-tech-in-human-patient-for-the-first-time.html">CNBC</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/26/u-s-house-of-representatives-accuses-musk-of-securities-fraud/life-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">馬斯克被指控涉嫌誤導投資者，指其淡化 Neuralink 植入晶片實驗憂慮</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/30/neuralink-first-implant-of-chips-in-human-brain/fun-tech/">Neuralink 首宗人類大腦植入晶片手術   Elon Musk：患者狀況良好 + 技術有前景</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
